{"tid":362353,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"條女變質定我問題？","createTime":"2017-08-17T00:24:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T12:25:39.000Z","uid":137647,"like":14,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f864a14c7de839a1980dffa1e238e6702129ea1d","tid":362353,"uid":137647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:24:02.000Z","msg":"同女友識左3年，之後一齊左2年<br />\n開頭都無啦野，平時一個星期上黎4日左右<br />\n但今年年頭佢就開始唔番工<br />\n話番工累，想放下假，之後就無再做<br />\n咁我都無所謂既，佢決定自己條路喱<br />\n但佢一放就放到左幾個月<br />\n叫佢番工又話就暑假難搵工<br />\n佢重要變左長期係我到住<br />\n平時我番工佢就陪我阿媽行街同自己打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢屋企人講，佢地笑笑口話辛苦哂照顧佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢d仆街親戚講野又難聽，佢地係我面前同條女講：係就快d結婚，唔係就分手搵過個啦<br />\n有次真係忍唔住話想散，佢先去搵份工，同自己搬番d野番屋企<br />\n到最後無散，諗住比多次機會佢<br />\n過左1個月即係易家<br />\n佢有搵我，但我感覺愈來愈淡<br />\n好多時都唔再想理佢<br />\n雖然佢有番工，但感覺佢改得太遲<br />\n<br />\n重有其他野<br />\n<br />\n佢有話有諗過做朋友可能重開心<br />\n易家基本上唔想搞佢，因為有次感覺到佢係明顯為出火而同我做<br />\n成日問我幾時同佢結婚<br />\n無番工又係咁買野，有時重要問我借錢，當然最後係無還啦，之後已無再借<br />\n成日屌其他人有咩野唔好，但自己做番同樣既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日話自己識邊個名人，其實只係佢以前老闆d fd<br />\n成日明明自己唔識又要衝出黎柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 特別係同佢去朋友飯局果陣，好多時都幫佢兜，喊出黎真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過佢有好多好既地方<br />\n性格好，好少發脾氣，但一發就仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 西面西足一日<br />\n會陪我阿媽行街。連悶到pk既地方佢都可以<br />\n專一，最多j下d韓星（我就唔鐘意韓星，佢會等自己一個先J)<br />\n唔會叫我送野俾佢，就算過時過節都可以平平淡淡咁過（不過好多時我都照送，或者整野食俾佢）<br />\n<br />\n其實最大問題係佢突然變到唔番工要我養埋果刻開始，所有感情愈來愈淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好大壓力，唔知佢咩心態<br />\n同佢傾完佢聽完就算，同咪佢同佢d屋企人成日講結婚真係好煩<br />\n<br />\n講番少少我自己<br />\n有車有樓，基本買貴野唔會肉痛，但平時少用錢。唔食煙但飲酒，無出去玩，技術宅一個。"},{"pid":"9e15606300390ce53aaa5e80e500c47f2ad8e54a","tid":362353,"uid":137647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:24:57.000Z","msg":"慘，打打下原來篇野咁長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77ac1405ec9648fe87f2de3fee38fd1d383fc59","tid":362353,"uid":90178,"like":28,"dislike":4,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:26:43.000Z","msg":"飬埋佢有咩問題？"},{"pid":"40b42996c388171c0a4abe04485a87ae76d56bf2","tid":362353,"uid":121676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:27:10.000Z","msg":"我女朋友性格同你個個有啲似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d701a4fcf65846477e1744ea23f7f967b0ae9b","tid":362353,"uid":90178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:27:11.000Z","msg":"你係窮定廢"},{"pid":"1d8237eff37c92c8eb567d78fcc2e69bdbe38974","tid":362353,"uid":99418,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:28:16.000Z","msg":"講到尾覺得你只係唔想養埋佢"},{"pid":"a87083c444c26a91ea363cc846f929dd67af0188","tid":362353,"uid":121676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:28:59.000Z","msg":"不過好彩佢唔做野都冇咩影響<br />\n佢而家都係搵緊一萬頭<br />\n比啲錢佢呀媽 其他都我搞掂"},{"pid":"2497091a03c66aa2ac297798606b4c879f107cb0","tid":362353,"uid":137647,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:29:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飬埋佢有咩問題？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢真係一日三餐衣食住行洗費都我出哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得結左婚就應該咁<br />\n但目前重拍緊拖就要包養埋佢<br />\n成個感覺似養多個人多過拍拖"},{"pid":"f4c6d8c34b390d753345a3dc0086a037f819d0d4","tid":362353,"uid":137647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:30:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我女朋友性格同你個個有啲似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你有咩諗法？"},{"pid":"a919285a167009e9d71f8b0fe5dc5a50a2ead0aa","tid":362353,"uid":10454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:30:50.000Z","msg":"分手啦<br />\n條女寵慣左<br />\n如果繼續落去你同佢一齊就預左要一份糧養兩個人"},{"pid":"8fe3909a933f7c17c5b2ccf6a474a79cf043cc2a","tid":362353,"uid":70962,"like":14,"dislike":8,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:31:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>飬埋佢有咩問題？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢真係一日三餐衣食住行洗費都我出哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得結左婚就應該咁<br />\n但目前重拍緊拖就要包養埋佢<br />\n成個感覺似養多個人多過拍拖</blockquote><br />\n有能力咪養埋囉，有問題？你無能力就同佢講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67868f5f89ebf05332a8d33fa37316177ff18796","tid":362353,"uid":137647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:32:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係窮定廢</blockquote><br />\n生活環境還好，各方面技能都ok"},{"pid":"f29360e0bec846b9d5625ff9c2823b5e3b1022d6","tid":362353,"uid":137647,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:33:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講到尾覺得你只係唔想養埋佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其一啦<br />\n我覺得雙方都有付出先叫拍拖，無論係錢定感情<br />\n單方面易家搞到好似我包養條女番黎咁"},{"pid":"7d07418678f7fd056031f637490ea5ba4b05ab00","tid":362353,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:34:26.000Z","msg":"當養隻私家雞囉"},{"pid":"fbc192c8456bec2d8e4bde5943788e0ab0bd4d82","tid":362353,"uid":137647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:34:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過好彩佢唔做野都冇咩影響<br />\n佢而家都係搵緊一萬頭<br />\n比啲錢佢呀媽 其他都我搞掂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔記得講埋佢係無比家用"},{"pid":"ac079796071fa73ddf490e76544ff71922aad4fe","tid":362353,"uid":137647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:38:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當養隻私家雞囉</blockquote><br />\n我老豆都係咁差講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我又無呢d想法，都唔鐘意咁<br />\n同咪好少搞一個月得一兩次左右"},{"pid":"95228be65be82baab5be6af58531acd58b2dcc90","tid":362353,"uid":45374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:39:02.000Z","msg":"條女靚唔靚先？<br />\n靚又專一可以養下，當婚後生活提早。<br />\n唔靚就分啦，反正你都對佢冇感覺。"},{"pid":"d5d90c8a8377aca68a0768235e518e9eb689f62d","tid":362353,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:41:04.000Z","msg":"我有俾你屌㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b9ce9f1586778bef6daf1b5bc332171d7654a5","tid":362353,"uid":2795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:44:22.000Z","msg":"好撚gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2365cfa8bc14e9d84084cb74ef9c4fe5d13565","tid":362353,"uid":45147,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:48:11.000Z","msg":"出火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ngay post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1dd18acf62c82a1650be83466377550f749f17","tid":362353,"uid":31824,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T01:05:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講番少少我自己<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有車有樓，基本買貴野唔會肉痛</span>，但平時少用錢。唔食煙但飲酒，無出去玩，技術宅一個。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁既條件都唔肯照顧條女，你都係算啦咁<br />\n佢都陪你阿媽，都算係返工一部份<br />\n<br />\n你都係想搵個籍口散姐"},{"pid":"bfcd8f25b53837ec363f02f10cd0969f8434e4a6","tid":362353,"uid":71096,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T01:16:27.000Z","msg":"係你問題啦，人地同你做左噤多野你就覺得無返工偷懶？行奶奶政策有問題？除非你養唔到佢都唔出來做野就係佢問題啫。個個女人都有情緒啦，難道你就無？你唔要人就早Ｄ出聲，你晒緊條女為左係你屋企的時間。記得補償番最低工資俾佢"},{"pid":"c024f5d48a5bc7cf85fc117695da2b29da558a17","tid":362353,"uid":96402,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T01:20:51.000Z","msg":"其實冇話邊個問題嘅<br />\n只不過係行咗咁耐 <br />\n你最近先發現你條女想要嘅生活嘅方式同你想要嘅唔同啫<br />\n自己覺得唔對路嘅咪同條女傾下囉<br />\n傾完佢肯改但你又覺得太遲 <br />\n覺得佢已經變咗<br />\n咁其實無論佢宜家用邊個方式生活<br />\n從你言語間都知你心入面有答案啦"},{"pid":"a042851809f26f5e961ac22f347341150dedf1e1","tid":362353,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3